review: I purchased these tabs because they are durable and last a long time. I needed to organize hundreds of pages worth of anatomy notes, and these tabs did the job. (I only say this because I could've easily gotten the paper ones for 99 cents, but they rip so easily and usually within a month)
productTitle: Avery  Big Tab Insertable Plastic Dividers,  8-Tabs, 1 Set (11901)
